<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='419000' id='t-419000'>Twenty-four European rabbits</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='421000' id='t-421000'>were brought to Australia in 1859</span>
